    "However, 42% of the summaries exhibited hallucinations and 47% omitted clinically relevant information.",
    "This compares to 36% of GPT-3.5-turbo summaries containing an inaccuracy, with 64% and 50% of the predecessor model's summaries containing hallucinations and clinical omissions, respectively.",
